    <item>
      <title>泰国大麻政策大转变 关键政党称这是人民的“胜利”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/thai-cannabis-policy-u-turn-a-victory-for-people-key-party-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国搁置重新将大麻定为犯罪的计划、转而加强监管的举措是“人民的胜利”，该政党的领导人表示，该政党因两年前率先实现具有里程碑意义的大麻非刑事化而受到广泛赞誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/thai-cannabis-policy-u-turn-a-victory-for-people-key-party-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 10:17:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
